---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro'
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '')
---
<Layout seo={{ title: 'About', description: 'Our story and values. Why we started Paroysia.' }}>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-cloud">About Paroysia</h1>

    <div class="mt-12">
      <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
        I come from enterprise technology — SAP systems, complex integrations, the kind of software that runs large organizations. Over the years, I also built a network of talented people. Designers, cinematographers — professionals who take their craft seriously. Paroysia exists because of that combination.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed mt-6">
        Too many small businesses get left behind by agencies quoting €5,000+ for a basic website — agencies that treat every client like a corporate account and don't understand what a small business actually needs.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed mt-6">
        You don't need enterprise budgets to get quality results. Just honest work, clear communication, and technology that serves your business — not the other way around.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="mt-16 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur text-cloud p-8 rounded-lg border border-slate/30">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Ready to partner with us?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-slate">Start with a free audit. See exactly where your business stands online.</p>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <a href={`${base}/free-audit`} class="inline-block bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded font-semibold hover:bg-deepgreen transition-colors">
          Get Your Free Audit
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>
</Layout>
